General Information

Ural Daily Supplement High Strength Cranberry 60,000mg is a concentrated on-a-day cranberry formula that suports urinary tract health and may reduce the risk and frequency of cystitis.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional.
If pain or irritation persists for more than 48 hours consult your doctor. The presence of blood in the urine warrants immediate medical attention.

Common Uses

A small, easy to swallow capsule that provides a high strength concentrated daily dose of cranberry. Cranberries reduce harmful bacteria from sticking to the urinary tract wall and may reduce the risk and frequency of cystitis.

Ingredients

Each capsule contains 60,000mg of blended Active Cranberry Extracts (ACE)

Directions

Adults and children 12 years and over.
One capsule daily with food or as directed by a healthcare professional.
